Package jdk.test.lib.hotspot.ir_framework

Annotation Interface DontCompile

@Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface DontCompile
Prevent a compilation of the annotated helper method (not specifying @Test, @Check or @Run):

  • CompLevel.ANY (default): No C1 or C2 compilation.

  • CompLevel.C1: No C1 compilation, C2 compilation still possible.

  • CompLevel.C2: No C2 compilation, C1 compilation still possible.

  • The usage of any other compilation level is forbidden and results in a TestFormatException.

Using this annotation on non-helper methods results in a TestFormatException.
